 actor for base-metal casting/plating/finishing lines producing
 finished costume/fashion jewellery and related articles (rings/
 chains/pendants/bracelets/earrings in zinc-alloy/brass/copper/
 nickel-silver/stainless-steel, gold-, silver- or rhodium-plated) --
 not direct casting/plating-line-equipment control authority and not a
